<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.4.5">
<l>kōmaḷa vāṉkaṉṟaip pulkik kōvintaṉ mēyttaṉa veṉṉum,</l>
<l>pōmiḷa nākattiṉ piṉpō yavaṉkiṭak kaiyī teṉṉu</l>
<l>māmaḷa voṉṟu maṟiyē ṉaruviṉai yāṭṭiyēṉ peṟṟa</l>
<l>kōmaḷa valliyai māyōṉ mālceytu ceykiṉṟa kūttē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Embracing a tender pure calf she says “Kōvintaṉ grazed them”,</l>
<l>going after a young serpent that goes she says “this [is] his couch”.</l>
<l>I do not know at all the measure to which will come the dance [she] does, caused by Māl,</l>
<l>by the Dark one to the tender creeper begotten by me [who is] a woman of difficult Karma.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
